v 1.7.0
---------

* Added: Mayorships are back!
* Added: Mayor crown added to checkin stream
* Added: Mayor crown and stickers added to check-in confirmation
* Added: Settings for default view on startup
* Added: Settings for pull to refresh behaviour
* Changed: The recent activity stream now has better data
* Changed: Searching for check-in venues has been optimised
* Changed: Not finding your current position now shows an error
* Fixed: Uploading images with check-ins is now more reliable
* Fixed: When searching for a check-in venue, the error message does not stay from before
* Fixed: Scene cover works now after reloading check-ins


v 1.6.1
---------

* Fixed: Checkins without stickers work again
